Ashley Roberts has sparked a frenzy after sharing bikini-clad snaps of herself as she enjoys a holiday abroad. In view of her 702,000 Instagram followers, the Heart FM presenter, 40, donned a strapless purple bikini which flaunted her fabulous figure as she held her face up towards the sun. Ashley captioned the snap: "'I own 51% of this pool'", alongside a purple heart and palm tree emoji. Days ago, the star posted a series of pictures from Marbella, Spain, which saw her pose up a storm in a hot pink bikini. Ashley looked happy and healthy as she leaned against a car while showing off her scultped figure.